@CalculatorApi_HostAddress = http://localhost:5113

### Add
GET {{CalculatorApi_HostAddress}}/api/calculate/add?num1=3&num2=4
Accept: application/json

### Subtract
GET {{CalculatorApi_HostAddress}}/api/calculate/subtract?num1=10&num2=3
Accept: application/json

### Multiply
GET {{CalculatorApi_HostAddress}}/api/calculate/multiply?num1=6&num2=7
Accept: application/json

### Divide
GET {{CalculatorApi_HostAddress}}/api/calculate/divide?num1=15&num2=3
Accept: application/json

### Divide by zero (expects 400)
GET {{CalculatorApi_HostAddress}}/api/calculate/divide?num1=5&num2=0
Accept: application/json

### POST calculate
POST {{CalculatorApi_HostAddress}}/api/calculate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "number1": 10,
  "number2": 2,
  "operation": "Divide"
}
